sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant SC as SessionController
    participant Hub as EventHub
    participant Pool as AgentPool

    Note over SC: === close() while busy ===

    Client->>SC: close()
    SC->>Hub: run_completed(cancelled)
    SC->>Hub: clearRunBuffer()
    SC->>Pool: kill(handle)
    SC->>SC: record.status = terminated
    SC->>Hub: session_status_changed(busy→terminated, user_closed)
    SC->>Hub: close()
    Hub-->>Client: stream ends

    Note over SC: === agent crash while busy ===

    Pool-->>SC: handleCrash()
    SC->>Hub: run_completed(cancelled)
    SC->>Hub: clearRunBuffer()
    SC->>SC: record.status = terminated
    SC->>Hub: session_status_changed(busy→terminated, agent_crashed)
    SC->>Hub: close()
    Hub-->>Client: stream ends

    Note over SC: Guarantee: run_completed ALWAYS before session_status_changed
